{"application": "software-mentions", "version": "0.8.0", "date": "2024-03-21T09:56+0000", "md5": "109A2899AD39078A311D815CDB90A3AE", "mentions": [{"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "WND-CHARM", "normalizedForm": "WND-CHARM", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 9}, "language": {"rawForm": "C++", "normalizedForm": "C++"}, "context": "WND-CHARM is a multi-purpose image classifier developed in C++, generating a high-dimension features-vector and using Weighted Neighbour Distances for classification [44]. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.0001246929168701172}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.00743025541305542}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999806880950928}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.10004311800003052}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 0, "offsetEnd": 13}, "context": "CellCognition dataset was used (see Methods \u00a72.1).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999109506607056}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 5.0067901611328125e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "WND-CHARM", "normalizedForm": "WND-CHARM", "offsetStart": 4, "offsetEnd": 13}, "language": {"rawForm": "C++", "normalizedForm": "C++"}, "context": "The WND-CHARM library contains a broad range of features, and we believe that most of the problems analysing biological images will find some appropriate. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.00012242794036865234}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.0018685460090637207}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999806880950928}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.10004311800003052}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "RTrees", "normalizedForm": "RTrees", "offsetStart": 22, "offsetEnd": 28}, "context": "To do so, we used the RTrees module using the OpenCV library [66]. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.999945878982544}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.2993812561035156e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.999945878982544}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.2993812561035156e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 40, "offsetEnd": 53}, "context": "We built a first image database (termed CellCognition) from the CellCognition [40] software demonstration images.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.32635360956192017}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "WND-CHARM", "normalizedForm": "WND-CHARM", "offsetStart": 42, "offsetEnd": 51}, "language": {"rawForm": "C++", "normalizedForm": "C++"}, "context": "Computing all the features offered by the WND-CHARM library for a 71 \u00d7 71 vignette on the ARM microcontroller was too computationally intensive for several features (Fig. 2a), thus incompatible with real-time analysis. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.836784303188324}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 9.417533874511719e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999806880950928}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.10004311800003052}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "OpenCV", "normalizedForm": "OpenCV", "offsetStart": 46, "offsetEnd": 52}, "context": "To do so, we used the RTrees module using the OpenCV library [66]. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.999945878982544}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.2993812561035156e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.999945878982544}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9828045964241028}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "[66]", "normalizedForm": "[66]", "refKey": 66, "offsetStart": 32335, "offsetEnd": 32339}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "WND-CHARM", "normalizedForm": "WND-CHARM", "offsetStart": 51, "offsetEnd": 60}, "language": {"rawForm": "C++", "normalizedForm": "C++", "wikidataId": "Q2407", "offsetStart": 59, "offsetEnd": 62}, "context": "Importantly, we performed some optimisation of the WND-CHARM library to reduce its execution time.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999806880950928}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.10004311800003052}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999806880950928}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.10004311800003052}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 58, "offsetEnd": 71}, "context": "We averaged over the 5-fold cross-validation and used the CellCognition dataset (see Methods \u00a72.1).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999712705612183}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.3113021850585938e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 64, "offsetEnd": 77}, "context": "We tested Fisher's linear-discriminant classification using the CellCognition dataset (see Methods \u00a72.1), in particular, 80% of the vignettes for training and 20% for testing through a k-fold cross-validation process (k = 5).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 4.76837158203125e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 64, "offsetEnd": 82}, "context": "We built a first image database (termed CellCognition) from the CellCognition [40] software demonstration images. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": false, "score": 0.32635360956192017}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 71, "offsetEnd": 84}, "context": "The converse experiment, using a mitocheck-trained network to classify CellCognition images, was not better, displaying a 42% accuracy and AUC equals to 0.50.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999397993087769}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 8.821487426757812e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "OpenCV library", "normalizedForm": "OpenCV library", "offsetStart": 74, "offsetEnd": 88}, "context": "We embedded our neural network using activation functions provided by the OpenCV library. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.999690055847168}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.13429081439971924}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 7.152557373046875e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.999690055847168}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.13429081439971924}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 7.152557373046875e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "WND-CHARM", "normalizedForm": "WND-CHARM", "offsetStart": 78, "offsetEnd": 91}, "language": {"rawForm": "C++", "normalizedForm": "C++"}, "context": "Along that line, we here used a wide variety of features found in the library WND-CHARM [44]. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9966670870780945}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 5.137920379638672e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999806880950928}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.10004311800003052}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 79, "offsetEnd": 92}, "context": "We tested the classification of mitocheck images with the network trained over CellCognition.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999940395355225}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 6.258487701416016e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 89, "offsetEnd": 102}, "context": "To support the development, we set to classify mitotic images within 8 classes using the CellCognition example set [40,48] (see Methods \u00a72.1).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.5438992977142334}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 0.07773000001907349}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "OpenCV", "normalizedForm": "OpenCV", "offsetStart": 94, "offsetEnd": 100}, "context": "For the sake of simplicity, in a proof-of-concept perspective, we trained the algorithm using OpenCV on the embedded system. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9998672008514404}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9828045964241028}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.999945878982544}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9828045964241028}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-07}}, "references": [{"label": "[66]", "normalizedForm": "[66]", "refKey": 66}]}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 94, "offsetEnd": 107}, "context": "TA B L E 1 Bootstrapping random forests optimal feature-groups-number classification over the CellCognition dataset.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9991689920425415}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.337860107421875e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 94, "offsetEnd": 107}, "context": "The feature groups appearing only in the optimal cases using this dataset (and not when using CellCognition) were italicised (Tab.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999098777770996}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 4.76837158203125e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 111, "offsetEnd": 124}, "context": "The feature-groups finally used in classification vary in the different instances of the bootstrap as with the CellCognition dataset without considerably impacting the execution time and the classification quality (Fig. 6).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9259875416755676}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.5033950805664062e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 137, "offsetEnd": 150}, "context": "To estimate the computing time of a single WND-CHARM feature, we computed it over the single-cell vignettes obtained, for instance, from CellCognition database, running on an NVIDIA Jetson AGX Xavier embedded system.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999891519546509}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 1.3589859008789062e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 149, "offsetEnd": 162}, "context": "To do so, we built a simple convolutional neural network, including 3 convolutional layers separated by relu activation layers and trained it on the CellCognition images using Keras.", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9697931408882141}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.984175980091095}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 151, "offsetEnd": 164}, "context": "This approach was repeated 10 times in the bootstrap approach, where the vignettes included in the balanced dataset were selected differently from the CellCognition (see Methods \u00a72.1).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9924322366714478}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 3.5762786865234375e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 1.1920928955078125e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "software", "software-name": {"rawForm": "CellCognition", "normalizedForm": "CellCognition", "offsetStart": 189, "offsetEnd": 202}, "context": "(d) The confusion matrix and (e) the ROC curves averaged using the 5-fold cross-validation in the optimal case of the twelve-feature-groups without computationally intensive ones using the CellCognition dataset (see \u00a72.1).", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999924898147583}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 5.125999450683594e-06}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9999946355819702}, "created": {"value": true, "score": 0.9907421469688416}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}, {"type": "software", "software-type": "environment", "software-name": {"rawForm": "Matlab", "normalizedForm": "Matlab", "offsetStart": 236, "offsetEnd": 242}, "context": "Conversely, Random forests were much slower than the neural network to be trained: training 300 decision trees using Random forests with 127 samples (80 % of the whole dataset) and 264 features (the 12 best feature-groups) took 21 s on Matlab using one CPU while training our neural network needed between 1 to 6 s. ", "mentionContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9987854361534119}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.0384788513183594e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}, "documentContextAttributes": {"used": {"value": true, "score": 0.9987854361534119}, "created": {"value": false, "score": 2.0384788513183594e-05}, "shared": {"value": false, "score": 2.384185791015625e-07}}}], "references": [{"refKey": 66, "tei": "<biblStruct xml:id=\"b66\">\n\t<monogr>\n\t\t<title/>\n\t\t<author>\n\t\t\t<persName><surname>Itseez</surname></persName>\n\t\t</author>\n\t\t<imprint>\n\t\t\t<date>2015</date>\n\t\t\t<publisher>Source Computer Vision Library</publisher>\n\t\t</imprint>\n\t</monogr>\n</biblStruct>\n"}], "runtime": 99310, "id": "d241a2e0cfac131a8843861c7ce07a01c60a58f5", "metadata": {"id": "d241a2e0cfac131a8843861c7ce07a01c60a58f5"}, "original_file_path": "../../datalake/Samuel/SV22/SV22_xml/hal-03408803.grobid.tei.xml", "file_name": "hal-03408803.grobid.tei.xml"}